<L>__{interior george & doris' house day}
<D>__{we see several quick sequences which indicate time passing: breakfasts with george and doris where the atmosphere is increasingly dreadful. doris scribbles on photos of george in the press, draws on moustaches, large spectacles, etc.}
<L>__{interior studio stages pirate cowboy etc. day}
<D>__{short extracts of george in various films, in which he portrays a pirate, then a cowboy, then william tell, etc. we also see him in "someday in july" in the sequence he shot with peppy and the fat male dancer.}
